{"tid":672251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他像狗狂嗅妻子！　稱有「小王味」竟這樣做","createTime":"2018-05-20T22:54:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T23:40:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ac90e4cbde3ba78cb5308428532fc037223e9c","tid":672251,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T22:54:07.000Z","msg":"張姓男子懷疑林姓妻子外遇，每當林女下班回家，他就像狗一樣，繞著林女聞她身體味道，還咬定她在外面偷吃，將她反鎖房內。林女報警控訴違反通常保護令，新竹地院日前依違反保護令判張男拘役80天，易科罰金8萬元。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，林女指控，去年張男家暴，她聲請保護令，去年3月新竹地院核發通常保護令，裁定張男不得對妻子精神與身體上不法侵害，為期1年，沒想到張男反而疑神疑鬼。<br />\n<br />\n林女下班回家，張就要她站好不許動，然後像狗一樣張鼻貼近她，繞著她狂嗅，林女大喊「你在幹什麼！你瘋了嗎！」張男問「去哪了？是不是剛從汽車旅館回來？」揚言能聞到外面男人，或汽車旅館的味道，咬定她在外面偷吃，將她反鎖房間，她只好報警。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180521/640_a7ef6f3c60a355b35808b7d019a09b5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180521%2F640_a7ef6f3c60a355b35808b7d019a09b5b.jpg&h=7ecd0887&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180521/1357784/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180521%2F1357784%2F&d=roPBnFQFRfcH9bYbT%2BtJnf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b6829b81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180521%2F1357784%2F&h=e23d94ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180521/1357784/</a>"},{"pid":"bdffa0cb718dede30df48c62d8951938b420b55c","tid":672251,"uid":51717,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T23:32:46.000Z","msg":"最撚憎呢種標籤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n標題應該簡潔易明<br />\n<br />\n而家啲網站最後撚鍾意呢類講啲唔講啲，點知連報紙都淪陷埋，毒果真係文化毒藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa7e8f3c0b6539620914e5586c1089d0d3094d2","tid":672251,"uid":25367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3